Text: These are great, I remember the promo cds in these.  Much better that they are FLAC (than mp3 or ape) and I am interested in 1989-1999 primarily, so these fill in my alt. 90s collection nicely.   Thank you for doing these.

Yes, thanks for these! A few months ago a kind soul at Demonoid upped most of these comps in flac... do a search you will find. I also uploaded 4 discs too. If you have anymore please do make available!

Kit
